<h4>Day 4: Start your day with one small victory: make your bed.</h4>
<blockquote class="instagram-media" style="background: #FFF; border: 0; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: 0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width: 658px; padding: 0; width: calc(100% - 2px);" data-instgrm-captioned="" data-instgrm-version="5">
<div style="padding: 8px;">
<div style="background: #F8F8F8; line-height: 0; margin-top: 40px; padding: 37.5% 0; text-align: center; width: 100%;"></div>
<p style="margin: 8px 0 0 0; padding: 0 4px;"><a href="https://instagram.com/p/8bHN6rIyCh/" onclick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'outbound-article', 'https://instagram.com/p/8bHN6rIyCh/', '#MinimalismTips Day 4: Start your day with one small victory: make your bed. An early-morning achievement sets the tone for the rest of your day, establishes a pattern of success, and leads to a more productive day overall. Plus, when you return home in the evening, you\'ll be greeted by a tidier, calmer bedroom. A successful day begins with your first win. What other small victories help you start your day on the right foot?']);" style="color: #000; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 17px; text-decoration: none; word-wrap: break-word;"  target="_blank">#MinimalismTips Day 4: Start your day with one small victory: make your bed. An early-morning achievement sets the tone for the rest of your day, establishes a pattern of success, and leads to a more productive day overall. Plus, when you return home in the evening, you&#8217;ll be greeted by a tidier, calmer bedroom. A successful day begins with your first win. What other small victories help you start your day on the right foot?</a></p>
<p style="color: #c9c8cd; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px; margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 8px; overflow: hidden; padding: 8px 0 7px; text-align: center; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap;">A photo posted by The Minimalists (@theminimalists) on <time style="font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px;" datetime="2015-10-04T17:13:14+00:00">Oct 4, 2015 at 10:13am PDT</time></p>
