<h4>Day 5: Establish a simple morning ritual.</h4>
<blockquote class="instagram-media" style="background: #FFF; border: 0; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: 0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width: 658px; padding: 0; width: calc(100% - 2px);" data-instgrm-captioned="" data-instgrm-version="5">
<div style="padding: 8px;">
<div style="background: #F8F8F8; line-height: 0; margin-top: 40px; padding: 50.0% 0; text-align: center; width: 100%;"></div>
<p><a href="https://instagram.com/p/8di3CQoyEC/" onclick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'outbound-article', 'https://instagram.com/p/8di3CQoyEC/', '#MinimalismTips Day 5: Establish a simple morning ritual. After making your bed (yesterday\'s tip), find five activities you\'d like to focus on during the next hour. Realize that you likely won\'t have time for all five, but if you spend time on at least two activities, then you\'ve won the morning. Then, tomorrow, focus on two different activities; continue alternating each day. In time, these daily rituals will turn into habits that lead to a highly productive and rewarding day. For us, our five habits include meditating, stretching, reading, writing, and exercise. Afterward, a good cup of coffee is a nice reward. What is your morning ritual? Are there new habits you\'d like to establish?']);" style="color: #000; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 17px; text-decoration: none; word-wrap: break-word;"  target="_blank">#MinimalismTips Day 5: Establish a simple morning ritual. After making your bed (yesterday&#8217;s tip), find five activities you&#8217;d like to focus on during the next hour. Realize that you likely won&#8217;t have time for all five, but if you spend time on at least two activities, then you&#8217;ve won the morning. Then, tomorrow, focus on two different activities; continue alternating each day. In time, these daily rituals will turn into habits that lead to a highly productive and rewarding day. For us, our five habits include meditating, stretching, reading, writing, and exercise. Afterward, a good cup of coffee is a nice reward. What is your morning ritual? Are there new habits you&#8217;d like to establish?</a></p>
<p>A photo posted by The Minimalists (@theminimalists) on <time style="font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px;" datetime="2015-10-05T15:53:15+00:00">Oct 5, 2015 at 8:53am PDT</time>
</div>
</blockquote>
