<h4>Day 26: A life with less is an inherently tidy life.</h4>
<blockquote class="instagram-media" style="background: #FFF; border: 0; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: 0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width: 658px; padding: 0; width: calc(100% - 2px);" data-instgrm-captioned="" data-instgrm-version="5">
<div style="padding: 8px;">
<div style="background: #F8F8F8; line-height: 0; margin-top: 40px; padding: 37.5% 0; text-align: center; width: 100%;"></div>
<p style="margin: 8px 0 0 0; padding: 0 4px;"><a href="https://instagram.com/p/9TkHj4IyGb/" onclick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'outbound-article', 'https://instagram.com/p/9TkHj4IyGb/', '#MinimalismTips Day 26: A life with less is an inherently tidy life. By stripping down to the essentials, our days are simpler to manage. Be it our homes, our vehicles, or our relationships, when we let go of that which does not improve our lives, we are left with a life that\'s more manageable, and thus more enjoyable. Oh, and it sure is nice to come home to a perpetually clutterfree environment. Here\'s a tip: look around your home, your office, your car, and identify anything that does not make your life better. How would letting go improve your life overall?']);" style="color: #000; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 17px; text-decoration: none; word-wrap: break-word;"  target="_blank">#MinimalismTips Day 26: A life with less is an inherently tidy life. By stripping down to the essentials, our days are simpler to manage. Be it our homes, our vehicles, or our relationships, when we let go of that which does not improve our lives, we are left with a life that&#8217;s more manageable, and thus more enjoyable. Oh, and it sure is nice to come home to a perpetually clutterfree environment. Here&#8217;s a tip: look around your home, your office, your car, and identify anything that does not make your life better. How would letting go improve your life overall?</a></p>
