<h4>Day 29: More is less: the more stuff we have, the less we have.</h4>
<blockquote class="instagram-media" style="background: #FFF; border: 0; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: 0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width: 658px; padding: 0; width: calc(100% - 2px);" data-instgrm-captioned="" data-instgrm-version="5">
<div style="padding: 8px;">
<div style="background: #F8F8F8; line-height: 0; margin-top: 40px; padding: 62.5% 0; text-align: center; width: 100%;"></div>
<p><a href="https://instagram.com/p/9blKnhoyIL/" onclick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'outbound-article', 'https://instagram.com/p/9blKnhoyIL/', '#MinimalismTips Day 29: More is less. The more stuff we have, the less we have: Less time for the people we love. Less money to spend on experiences. Less focus on our health. Less ability to grow and contribute to the world around us. Less contentment. Less joy. Less value. Less meaning. Less intention. More stuff: less of what\'s truly important.']);" style="color: #000; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 17px; text-decoration: none; word-wrap: break-word;"  target="_blank">#MinimalismTips Day 29: More is less. The more stuff we have, the less we have: Less time for the people we love. Less money to spend on experiences. Less focus on our health. Less ability to grow and contribute to the world around us. Less contentment. Less joy. Less value. Less meaning. Less intention. More stuff: less of what&#8217;s truly important.</a></p>
